43
00:01:41,790 --> 00:01:42,950
He's going to come for you.

44
00:01:43,790 --> 00:01:45,150
Whatever happens, I can't see him.

45
00:01:45,790 --> 00:01:47,710
I used the worst way

46
00:01:47,870 --> 00:01:49,590
to convince Young Miss

47
00:01:49,590 --> 00:01:51,710
