55
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:21,150
She can't see you.

56
00:02:22,550 --> 00:02:24,180
(You'll get her in trouble.)

57
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:33,030
(Xiaodie,)

58
00:02:33,940 --> 00:02:35,310
(I want to see you so bad.)

59
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:42,660
(I'm so sorry.)

60
00:02:43,940 --> 00:02:46,990
(Guess it was a bad idea
to drag you into this whole mess.)

61
00:02:51,140 --> 00:02:53,740
♪In every word between us♪

62
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,590
(Nie Zhen...)

63
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:59,150
(I wish I could see you.)

64
00:03:01,110 --> 00:03:02,780
(And hold you in my arms.)

65
00:03:05,780 --> 00:03:08,620
(But until I come up
with a foolproof plan,)

66
00:03:10,110 --> 00:03:11,660
(my priority is to keep
you out of harm's way.)

67
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:17,030
(While it hurts like hell,)

68
00:03:18,990 --> 00:03:20,940
(watching you as you leave is
my only option.)

